"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-10-09-team-gb-superstar-opens-olympic-mistake-reduced-tears-21765234\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GBsuperstarDina Asher-Smithhas opened up about her 'mistake' at the 2024Olympic GamesinPariswhich saw her break down in tears.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith, who was aiming to land a medal in the women's 100m event, dramatically failed to qualify for the final after finishing fifth in the semi-finals.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old, a Diamond League champion over 100m in 2019, was reduced to tears when she spoke to the BBC about the race, admitting she was 'very upset'.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999998910880153, \"rank\": 1.0542788761913832e-07, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9926058843049056, \"rank\": 0.0070816250859221915, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now some time has passed, Asher-Smith has lifted the lid on the errors she made and admits she got her mental approach all wrong in the French capital.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9877178902285901, \"rank\": 0.012184979270162065, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I made a mistake,' Asher-Smith told theIndependent.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Then I corrected it, and went and did really well in the last three Diamond Leagues.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Sometimes it's just about the attitude and energy you bring to the start line.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Different emotional moods work for different people.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When you are in a new coaching set-up this is stuff that you figure out along the way.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Nobody in this life, including athletes, are perfect.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But all you can do when that happens is just to learn from it and not make the same mistake and keep it moving.'\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith has clinched three Olympic medals to date, which have all come in the team-based 4\\u00d7100m relay event.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside her teammates, Asher-Smith won silver at Paris 2024, improving on back-to-back bronze medals at Tokyo 2020 and Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith is still waiting to register her first individual Olympic medal despite her impressive tally at the European Championships and World Championships.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The British athlete's highest Olympic finish individually was fourth in the 200m at Paris 2024, missing a medal by two-hundredths of a second.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.938702004771128, \"rank\": 0.046512650047829944, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999972033, \"rank\": 2.7947404734955576e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith is a four-time individual European champion, including the 200m title in 2016 and the 100m/200m double in 2018.\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9969323111667733, \"rank\": 0.002580596167012976, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won the 100m title again this year.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Georgia Bell: Parkrun has taken me from low points to Paris Olympics podium  ArrowMORE:Team GB Olympics star reveals sensational offer to join WWE  ArrowMORE:Olympic champion suggests London should be bombed for Russia sanctions to end  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1915, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"